  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3458030/extras/b9de7d28c51ae3910d61aa7a939c6967.avif?t=1742605779\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3458030/extras_big/b9de7d28c51ae3910d61aa7a939c6967.avif?t=1742605779 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Introduction</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DescTop</strong> is a cozy typing game where you can type at your own pace, in your own speed, how ever you like. You can type the target word given to you or you can type your essay in the ingame notepad; whatever you type you will be rewarded for it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3458030/extras/b991545d665efbb08c2c2ef4d2b5fc36.poster.avif?t=1742605779\" width=800 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3458030/extras/b991545d665efbb08c2c2ef4d2b5fc36.webm?t=1742605779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3458030/extras/b991545d665efbb08c2c2ef4d2b5fc36.mp4?t=1742605779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main gameplay features in <strong>DescTop</strong> is: Type, Make money, spend money on upgrades, buy decorations, <strong>Glam your DeskTop!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3458030/extras/aced34e0d13158d604ba030f293dfe52.poster.avif?t=1742605779\" width=800 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3458030/extras/aced34e0d13158d604ba030f293dfe52.webm?t=1742605779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3458030/extras/aced34e0d13158d604ba030f293dfe52.mp4?t=1742605779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DescTop</strong> is a game meant to be played on the side. A <strong>digital fidget toy</strong> that you can use for self expression. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3458030/extras/b9de7d28c51ae3910d61aa7a939c6967.avif?t=1742605779\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3458030/extras_big/b9de7d28c51ae3910d61aa7a939c6967.avif?t=1742605779 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Introduction</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DescTop</strong> is a cozy typing game where you can type at your own pace, in your own speed, how ever you like. You can type the target word given to you or you can type your essay in the ingame notepad; whatever you type you will be rewarded for it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3458030/extras/b991545d665efbb08c2c2ef4d2b5fc36.poster.avif?t=1742605779\" width=800 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3458030/extras/b991545d665efbb08c2c2ef4d2b5fc36.webm?t=1742605779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3458030/extras/b991545d665efbb08c2c2ef4d2b5fc36.mp4?t=1742605779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main gameplay features in <strong>DescTop</strong> is: Type, Make money, spend money on upgrades, buy decorations, <strong>Glam your DeskTop!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3458030/extras/aced34e0d13158d604ba030f293dfe52.poster.avif?t=1742605779\" width=800 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3458030/extras/aced34e0d13158d604ba030f293dfe52.webm?t=1742605779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3458030/extras/aced34e0d13158d604ba030f293dfe52.mp4?t=1742605779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DescTop</strong> is a game meant to be played on the side. A <strong>digital fidget toy</strong> that you can use for self expression. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
